                <li>{% trans %}Motivating interactive content (I assure you it's true){% endtrans %}</li>
                <li>{% trans %}Automatic notation (it's still a real revolution){% endtrans %}</li>
                <li>{% trans %}Real-time activity tracking (receive student results by email){% endtrans %}</li>
                <li>{% trans %}Test your students via a smartphone and deliver live results at a presentation{% endtrans %}</li>
            </ul>
            <br>
            <p>{% trans %}License: It is a free software but paying, must not forget that we are a Capitalist country anyway{% endtrans %}</p>
